quran[147]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"CcekĂŽan i Ăebbi, Mass imavalen"
  1,2,AĂȘnin IpĂȘunun
  1,3,Agellid n wass iqeĂźĂźiyen
  1,4,"D KeĂ§Ă§ ay naĂąbed, d KeĂ§Ă§ ay nepper d AmĂąÂČiwen"
  1,5,Awi ya$ d ubrid iweqmen
  1,6,"Abrid n wid i T$atev; ur n wid i K isserfayen, ne$ n im$eĂŽĂŽqen"
  2,1,Alm
  2,2,"Appan Tezmamt, ur degs ccekk, d nnhaya i wid ipĂȘezziben"
  2,3,"wid iumnen s tbavnit, ipĂ©allan, ipseddiqen seg wayen iten N$at"
  2,4,"wid iumnen s wayen i k d irsen, akked wayen id irsen, uqbel ik, u, $ef laxeĂŽt, nitni, pputebbten"
  2,5,"Widak, di nnhaya n Mass nnsen, widak, d isaĂądiyen"
  2,6,"Wid ijehlen, s tidep, iĂąuva fellasen ma tnubav ten, ne$ ur ten tnubav. Ur ppamnen"
  2,7,"Isle$ Ăebbi ulawen nnsen, akked imeĂ©Ă©u$en nnsen. Irs le$yaĂŽ $ef allen nnsen. Fellasen aĂąaqeb abarar"
  2,8,"Ger yimdanen, llan wid iqqaĂŽen: \"numen s Ăebbi akked wass aneggaruâ; nitni, ur llin d lmumnin"
  2,9,"La xedĂąen Ăebbi akked wid iumnen. Ur xedĂąen siwa iman nnsen, ur faqen"
  2,10,"AĂźan deg ulawen nnsen; Irna yasen Ăebbi aĂźan. Fellasen aĂąaqeb aqeĂŽĂȘan, ilmend n wayen skiddiben"
  2,11,"Ma nnan asen: \"ur ssefsadet di tmurt\"! A d inin: \"nekwni d wid, kan, ipleqqimen"
  2,12,"Day maĂ§Ă§i d nitni, s tidep, ay d ifessaden, maca ur faqen"
  2,13,"Ma nnan asen: \"amnet, akken umnen medden\"! A d inin: \"day a namen, akken umnen ije$lufen\"? Day maĂ§Ă§i d nitni, s tidep, ay d ije$lufen, maca ur Ă©ĂŽin"
  2,14,"Ma mmugren d wid iumnen, ad inin: \"numen\". Mara yilin weĂȘĂȘedsen, ar ccwaĂźen nnsen, ad inin: \"nekwni yidwen! Nekwni la nettihi kan"
  2,15,Ăebbi ad Ittihi fellasen. Isnerna yasen lbwe$v nnsen; ddebdeben
  2,16,"Widak, d wid iu$en ttelfan s nnhaya; ur d issasay ssuq nnsen, ur pwanhan"
  2,17,"TevĂŽa yidsen am win issa$en times. Mi tnewweĂŽ ayen i s d izzin, Ăebbi Iddem tafat nnsen, Iooa ten di tillas, ur pwalin"
  2,18,"ĂaĂ©gen, gugmen, dre$len; ihi, nitni ur d ppu$alen s abrid"
  2,19,"Ne$ am usigna igenni, degs tillas, tirmegt, lebĂŽaq. Pparran ivudan nnsen deg imeĂ©Ă©u$en nnsen, mgal ssiĂąqat; ad nnestaĂŽen si tmeppant. Ăebbi Izzi i ijehliyen"
  2,20,"QĂŽib i sen iĂȘwi lebĂŽaq, iĂ©ĂŽi. Yal tikelt ideg i sen icĂąal, ad ddun syis. Mi sen ixsi, ad ĂȘebsen. Ma ihwa yaS i Ăebbi, ad asen Ikkes timesliwt akked yiĂ©ĂŽi nnsen. Ăebbi, s tidep, Izmer i yal cci"
  2,21,"A yimdanen! Ăabdet Mass nnwen ikwen Ixelqen, kunwi, akked wid i kwen id izwaren, amar a pĂȘezzbem"
  2,22,"i wen Irran tamurt d usu, igenni d lebni; id Isse$li d aman seg igenni, Issuffe$ ed yissen ppemĂŽa, d ĂŽĂŽeĂ©q i kunwi. Ihi, ur pparrat tanudda i Ăebbi, u kunwi teĂ©ĂŽam"
  2,23,"Ma tellam di ccekk, $ef wayen id Nessers ar umdan nneÂŁ, awit ed tasuĂŽep i p icban. Neccdet ed inagan nnwen, war Ăebbi, ma tessawalem tidep"
  2,24,"Ma ur tessawvem, u, war ccekk, ur tessawavem, ĂȘezzbet i tmes isseĂŽ$an imdanen, id$a$en, ippuheggan i ijehliyen"
  2,25,"BecceĂŽ wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, ar i nitni, leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Yal tikelt ara ppuĂŽeĂ©qen, si ppemĂŽa nnsen, ad inin: \"d aya is neppuĂŽeĂ©q, uqbel\". Ippunefk asen i ten icban. Din, jjwao nnsen d ayen iĂ»fan. Degsen ad wekkĂŽen"
  2,26,"Ih, ur Ikukra ara Ăebbi, a d Ifk amedya n tizip, ne$ ip i$elben. Wid iumnen Ă©ĂŽan neppa d tidep, s$uĂŽ Mass nnsen. Wanag wid ijehlen qqaĂŽen: \"acu Ib$a Ăebbi s umedya agi\"? Yis, Itellif aĂźas; yis, Inehhu aĂźas. Ur Itellif yis, siwa iballa$en"
  2,27,"wid ipĂŽuĂ©un lemĂąahda n Ăebbi, deffir lmitaq iS, issemfaĂŽaqen ayen id IumeĂŽ Ăebbi ad imlil, issefsaden di tmurt. Widak d imexsuĂŽen"
  2,28,"Amek ara tnekĂŽem Ăebbi? Tellam temmuten, Issader kwen id. Sinna, a kwen Ine$, sinna, a kwen id Issider, sinna, $uĂŽeS a ppu$alem"
  2,29,"D Neppa i wen Ixelqen ayen akw illan di tmurt; sinna, Izzi ar igenni, Iwqem it d Ă»a igenwan. Neppa, Issen yal cci"
  2,30,"Mi Inna Mass ik, i lmalayek: \"Nek ad Rre$ aneĂ»Ă»af di tmurt\". Nnant aS: \"day a Pperrev, degs, win ara isfesden degs, ara izzizlen idamen? Wanag, nekwenti nesbuccuĂą K s ccekĂŽan, u NeĂŽĂŽequ yaK\". Inna: \"Nek, ĂšĂŽi$ ayen ur teĂ©ĂŽimt"
  2,31,"IsseĂȘfev akw ismawen i Adem. Sinna, Issken iten i lmalayek, Inna: \"efkemt iyI d ismawen n wigi, ma kunemti d sut tidep"
  2,32,"Nnant: \"gedha s yisseK! Ur nessin, siwa i a$ Teslemdev. KeĂ§Ă§, s tidep, d Amusnaw, d Bab n Ă»Ă»wab"
  2,33,"Inna: \"a Adem, efk asent ismawen nnsen\". Mi sent imla ismawen nnsen, Inna: \"day ur a kwent Nni$ ara: Nek Ssne$ tabavnit n tmurt akked igenwan, u ĂšĂŽi$ ayen d teqqaĂŽem, akked wayen teppeffrem"
  2,34,"Mi Nenna i lmalayek: \"knumt i Adem\"! Knant, siwa Iblis. Iugi, u isme$weĂŽ iman is. Illa seg ijehliyen"
  2,35,"Nenna: \"a Adem, ezde$ keĂ§Ă§ akked tmeĂźĂźut ik, di Loennet, eĂ§Ă§et segs, s tawant, ayen i wen ihwan. Ur ppaĂ©et ar ttejĂŽa yagi, mulac a ppilim d imednas"
  2,36,"Ikellex iten CciĂźan fellas. Issuffe$ iten id seg wanda llan. Nenna: \"Ă»Ă»ubbet, d icenga bbwaygarawen. I kunwi, di tmurt, i$imi akked zzhu, siwa tallit"
  2,37,"Adem iĂźĂźef awalen n Mass is. Issuref as. Neppa, s tidep, Issuruf, IpĂȘunu"
  2,38,"Nenna: \"Ă»Ă»ubbet segs, akken ma tellam. War ccekk, a kwen id tas nnhaya s$uĂŽI\". Wid iddan d nnhaya, ur ppagwaden, ur $weblen"
  2,39,"Wid ijehlen u skaddben issekniyen nneÂŁ, widak d at tmes, degs ad wekkĂŽen"
  2,40,"A yAt IsĂŽail! Mmektit ed l$it iW, is ikwen ĂeĂ©qe$. EĂźĂźfet di lemĂąahda W, ad ĂĂźfe$ di lemĂąahda nnwen. D nek iwumi ara tĂȘezzbem"
  2,41,"Amnet s wayen id Sserse$, itebbten ayen illan $uĂŽwen. Ur ppilit d imezwura ara t iagwin. Ur ppa$et, s issekniyen iW, ayen ĂŽxisen. D nek iwumi ara tĂȘezzbem"
  2,42,"Ur slusut, i tidep, tikerkas. Ur teffret tidep, u kunwi teĂ©ĂŽam"
  2,43,"ĂšĂ©allet, zekkit, ĂźĂźinzet akked wid iĂźĂźinizen"
  2,44,"Day a ppamĂŽem ise$ i medden, a ppeppum iman nnwen? U kunwi teqqaĂŽem Tazmamt. Day ur tefhimem ara"
  2,45,"Ssutret lemĂąawna n Ă»Ă»beĂŽ akked tĂ©allit. Ih, dayen iwaĂąĂŽen, siwa i imeĂ©luven"
  2,46,"wid iĂȘĂ»an ar ad mlilen akked Mass nnsen, u $uĂŽeS, nitni, war ccekk, ad u$alen"
  2,47,"A yAt IsĂŽail! Mmektit ed l$it iW, is ikwen ĂeĂ©qe$. Nek, Smenyafe$ kwen i imavalen"
  2,48,"Ăezzbet i wass ideg ur ippuoazi yiwen deg umkan n wayev, s wacemma. Ur tepwaqbal ccafuĂąa segs, ur tepwaĂźĂźaf, segs, le$ĂŽama, ur ten ppaĂąwanen"
  2,49,"Mi kwen Nsellek seg ugdud n FerĂąun, sĂąaddayen fellawen aĂąaqeb adiran. Zellun arrac nnwen, ssidiren tilawin nnwen. Ayagi d taluft tabarart, s$uĂŽ Mass nnwen"
  2,50,"Mi, yiswen, NessemfaĂŽeq ill, Nsellek ikwen, Ne$meq agdud n FerĂąun, kunwi la tepwalim"
  2,51,"Mi Nga lemĂąahda i Musa, kuĂ©et wavan; sinna, deffir es, teddam d uĂąajmi. Kunwi d imednas"
  2,52,"Sinna, deffir waya, NsemmeĂȘ awen, amar a ppesnemmrem"
  2,53,"Mi Nefka, i Musa, Tazmamt akked ufraz, amar a ppeppwanhum"
  2,54,"Mi inna Musa i ugdud is: \"a yagdud iw! Kunwi, s tidep, tdensem iman nnwen, mi teddam d uĂąajmi. Ssutret ssmaĂȘ i Uxellaq nnwen; mmin$et, ppif i kunwi ar Uxellaq nnwen. Issuref awen. Neppa, s tidep, Issuruf, IpĂȘunu"
  2,55,"Mi tennam: \"a Musa! Ur neppamen yisek, d awez$i, alamma nwala Ăebbi, Ăąinani\". Tewwet ikwen id ssiĂąqa, kunwi tepwalim"
  2,56,"Sinna, Nerra kwen id, deffir tmeppant nnwen, amar a ppesnemmrem"
  2,57,"S usigna, Nerra yawen tili. Nessers awen d lmenna, ifeĂŽĂŽuoen: \"eĂ§Ă§et si tĂ©idanin is ikwen N$at\". Ur aÂŁ dnisen, maca densen iman nnsen"
  2,58,"Mi Nenna: \"kecmet tamdint agi, eĂ§Ă§et degs, s tawant, ayen i wen ihwan; kecmet si tebburt, s lekni; init: nendem. Ad awen NsemmeĂȘ tuccva nnwen, a Nernu i iĂąaĂŽviyen"
  2,59,"Wid idensen bedlen awal, ur d win i sen nnan. Nessers ed, i wid idensen, tawa$it seg igenni, ilmend n tucmitin nnsen"
  2,60,"Mi issuter Musa aman i ugdud is, Nenna: \"ewwet aĂ©ĂŽu, s uĂąkkwaz ik\". Feggvent ed, segs, mrawsnat tliwa. Yal wa iĂ©ĂŽa anda ara issew. \"EĂ§Ă§et, esswet, si ĂŽĂŽeĂ©q n Ăebbi. Ur ssefsadet di tmurt am imjaĂȘen"
  2,61,"Mi tennam: \"a Musa! Ur nesteqnaĂą bippa s yiwen n lqut. Nuj a$ Mass ik, ad a$ d Issuffe$ ayen d teggar tmurt: tizzegzewt is, axyaĂŽ is, ticcert is, laĂąds is, lebĂ»el is\". Inna: \"teb$am a pbedlem ayen ilhan s wayen ixuĂ»en? ĂĂ»ubbet ar MaĂ»eĂŽ, a n tafem, war ccekk, ayen tessutrem\". I$li d fellasen ddell akked Ă©Ă©elt. Sebbeben d urrif n Ăebbi. Ayagi, acku llan ugin issekniyen n Ăebbi, neqqen lambiyya, war ssebba. Ayagi, imi ĂąuĂ»an, u zgaren tilas"
  2,62,"Ih, wid iumnen, udayen, imasiĂȘiyen, iĂ»abiyen, kra iumnen s Ăebbi akked wass aneggaru, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, ad sĂąun arraz ar Mass nnsen, ur ppagwaden, ur $weblen"
  2,63,"Mi Nga laĂąqed yidwen, Nessuli adrar sennig wen: \"eĂźĂźfet nezzeh ayen i wen Nefka, mmektit ed i illan degs, amar a pĂȘezzbem"
  2,64,"Sinna, deffir waya, twexxĂŽem. Lemmer maĂ§Ă§i d lfevl n Ăebbi fellawen, akked uĂȘunu S, a ppilim seg imexsuĂŽen"
  2,65,"Ni$ tessnem wid, segwen, iccven di Ssebt. Nenna yasen: \"ilit d iddawen imaĂąfan"
  2,66,"Nerra p d amedya i imuddiren akked wid i ten id ineĂ»fen, u d aĂąggen i wid ipĂȘezziben"
  2,67,"Mi inna Musa i ugdud is: \"Ăebbi, s tidep, IumeĂŽ awen d a ppezlum tafunast\". Nnan: \"day a tettihiv fella$\"? Inna: \"ad iyi IsseĂŽ Ăebbi! Ur ppili$ seg at war tussna"
  2,68,"Nnan: \"nuj a$ ar Mass ik, ad a$ d Ibeggen anta p\". Inna: \"Neppa, s tidep, la IqqaĂŽ: tafunast ur wessret, ur meĂ©Ă©iyet, garasen. Xedmet i wen d ippumĂŽen"
  2,69,"Nnan: \"nuj ar Mass ik, ad a$ d Ibeggen ini s\". Inna: \"Neppa, s tidep, la IqqaĂŽ: d tafunast tawĂŽa$t, ini imfeooeo, ad iaĂąoeb w ip iwalan"
  2,70,"Nnan: \"nuj ar Mass ik, ad a$ d Ibeggen anta p. ÂŁuĂŽne$, s tidep, tistan ppemcabint. Ih, ma Ib$a Ăebbi, a nepwanhu"
  2,71,"Inna: \"Neppa, s tidep, la IqqaĂŽ: d tafunast ur taĂątib si tyerza n tmurt, ne$ si tissit n yigran, tĂ»eĂȘĂȘa, ur tepwacĂŽev\". Nnan as: \"tura, tebbwiv d tidep\". Zlan p. QĂŽib ur ewqimen"
  2,72,"Mi ten$am yiwen, wa irra p id $ef wa. Ăebbi Issuffe$ ed ayen teppeffrem"
  2,73,"Nenna: \"ewwtet ep s kra ines\". Akka i Issidir Ăebbi lmeggtin. IssenĂąat awen issekniyen iS, amar a pfehmem"
  2,74,"Sinna, deffir waya, qquĂŽen wulawen nnwen; cuban aĂ©ĂŽu, ne$ kteĂŽ, di ta$eĂŽt. Ih, llan iĂ©ĂŽa iseg d pfeggiven isaffen. Llan, s tidep, wid ipceqqiqen, teff$en d waman segsen. S tidep, llan wid i$ellin si tugwdi n Ăebbi. Ur I$fil Ăebbi $ef wayen txeddmem"
  2,75,"Day tĂŽe$bem a kwen amnen? Ni$ arbaĂą, segsen, ssemĂȘasen i wawal n Ăebbi, sinna, mi t fehmen, ad as bedlen udem, u nitni Ă©ĂŽan"
  2,76,"Mi mmugren wid iumnen, ad inin: \"numen\". Mi qqimen garasen, qqaĂŽen: \"day ad asen tinim ayen i wen Imla Ăebbi, a kwen nna$en yis, ar Mass nnwen? Day ur tepmeyyizem ara"
  2,77,"Ne$ ur Ă©ĂŽin ara, Ăebbi Issen ayen teffren, akked wayen qqaĂŽen"
  2,78,"Garasen, at war ta$uĂŽi, ur nessin Tazmamt, siwa ayen nnwan. Nitni $ilen kan"
  2,79,"A tawa$it n wid ipparun Tazmamt s ifassen nnsen, sinna, qqaĂŽen: \"ayagi s$uĂŽ Ăebbi\", iwakken ad a$en, yis, ayen ĂŽxisen! A tawa$it nnsen, ilmend n wayen uran ifassen nnsen! A tawa$it nnsen, $ef wayen keppben"
  2,80,"Nnan: \"ur a$ tepnal tmes, d awez$i, siwa kra n wussan\". Ini: \"day teĂźĂźfem lemĂąahda s$uĂŽ Ăebbi? Ăebbi, d awez$i, ur Izeggil lemĂąahda S. Ne$ teqqaĂŽem, $ef Ăebbi, ayen ur tessinem"
  2,81,"XaĂźi, win ikesben tucmip, u tennev as tuccva sâŠ, widak, d at tmes, degs ad wekkĂŽen"
  2,82,"Wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, widak, d at Loennet, degs ad wekkĂŽen"
  2,83,"Mi Nga laĂąqed i At IsĂŽail: \"ur Ăąabdet siwa Ăebbi. Elhut ar imawlan, ar llzem nnwen, ar igujilen, ar igellilen. Init i medden, awal imaĂąnen. ĂšĂ©Ăallet, zekkit\". Sinna, twexxĂŽem, siwa kra segwen, u, kunwi, tnumrem"
  2,84,"Mi wen Nga laĂąqed nnwen: \"ur zzazalet idim nnwen, ur pemssuffu$et seg ixxamen nnwen\". D$a twefqem, kunwi d inagan"
  2,85,"Sinna, kunwi d wid immin$en, tessuff$em arbaĂą segwen, seg ixxamen nnsen. Tezzim asen s ibekkaven akked taĂądawt. Ma usan kwen id, d imeĂȘbas, tfeddum ten. Irna, ipwagdel awen usuffe$ nnsen. Day tumnem deg uĂȘric n Tezmamt, tnekĂŽem wayev? Anwa ay d arraz n wid, segwen, ixedmen aya, ma maĂ§Ă§i d ddell, di tmeddurt n ddunit, u, ass n tnekra, ad ppunefken i uĂąaqeb uqsiĂȘ mavi? Ur I$fil Ăebbi $ef wayen txeddmem"
  2,86,"Widak d wid iu$en tudert n ddunit s laxeĂŽt, ur ippifsus fellasen uĂąaqeb, ur ppusellken"
  2,87,"Ni$ Nefka Tazmamt i Musa. Nuzen ed imazanen, deffir es. Nefka abeggen i Ăisa, mmi s n Meryem, Null it s ĂŽĂŽuĂȘ iqedsen. Yal tikelt ideg ara kwen id ias umazan, s wayen ur awen nehwi, tesme$wĂŽem iman nnwen. Kra teskaddbem ten, kra ten$am ten"
  2,88,"Nnan: \"ulawen nne$ qquĂŽen\". XaĂźi, Ixza ten Ăebbi, ilmend n tijehli nnsen. Drus iten wid iumnen"
  2,89,"Mi ten id tusa Tezmamt, s$uĂŽ Ăebbi, d atebbet n wayen illan $uĂŽsen, - u llan, iu$ lĂȘal, ssuturen ad $elben wid ijehlen - mi ten id iusa wayen ssnen, ugin t. Ad InĂąal Ăebbi ijehliyen"
  2,90,"I icmet wayen i$ef zzenzen iman nnsen! Ugin ayen id Issers Ăebbi. Ăesden mi id Issers Ăebbi, si lfevl iS, i win i S ihwan n yimdanen iS. Sebbeben urrif ar wayev. I ijehliyen, aĂąaqeb isdullun"
  2,91,"Ma nnan asen: \"amnet s wayen id Issers Ăebbi\"! A d inin: \"numen s wayen id irsen $uĂŽne$\". NekĂŽen ayen i t id itebĂąan, u neppa d tidep, d atebbet n wayen illan $uĂŽsen. Ini: \"acimi tneqqem lambiyya n Ăebbi, zik, ma d lmumnin ay tellam"
  2,92,"Ni$ iusa kwen id Musa, s ubeggen. Sinna, deffir es, teddam akked uĂąajmi. Kunwi d imednas"
  2,93,"Mi Nga laĂąqed yidwen, Nessuli adrar sennig wen: \"eĂźĂźfet nezzeh ayen i wen Nefka, u ssemĂȘesset\". Nnan d: \"nesla u nĂąuĂ»a\". Ikecm asen uĂąajmi ar wul, si tjehli nnsen. Ini: \"dir it wayen i wen iumeĂŽ liman nnwen, ma d lmumnin ay tellam"
  2,94,"Ini: \"maday, ar Ăebbi, axxam aneggaru i kunwi kan, ur pkkan ara imdanen, mennit tameppant, ma tessawalem tidep"
  2,95,"D awez$i, ur p pmennin, ilmend n wayen xedmen ifassen nnsen. Ăebbi Issen imednas"
  2,96,"A ten tafev, war ccekk, ĂȘemmlen tameddurt sennig medden, sennig imcurak. Atan yiwen segsen, issaram ad idder agim iseggwasen. Te$wzi n laĂąmeĂŽ is, ur as tessifrir aĂąaqeb. Ăebbi Ipwali ayen xeddmen"
  2,97,"Ini: \"anwa illan d acengu n Jebrayen\"? D neppa, s tidep, it id issersen $ef wul ik, s leb$i n Ăebbi. D atebbet n wayen it id izwaren, d nnhaya u d abecceĂŽ n lmumnin"
  2,98,"Win illan d acengu n Ăebbi, lmalayek iS, imazanen iS, Jebrayen, MikailâŠ, ihi, Ăebbi d acengu ijehliyen"
  2,99,"Ni$ Nessers ak d issekniyen iberrzen. I ten inekĂŽen, siwa iballa$en"
  2,100,"Day yal tikelt ideg ara gen laĂąqed, a t ixdaĂą urbaĂą segsen? Ih, tegwti segsen, ur uminen"
  2,101,"Mi ten id iusa umazan s$uĂŽ Ăebbi, itebbet ayen illan $uĂŽsen, arbaĂą n wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, rran Tazmamt n Ăebbi s azagur nnsen, amzun ur ssinen"
  2,102,"Ddan akked wayen xedmen ccwaĂźen mgal tagelda n Sliman. Sliman ur ijhil. Maca ccwaĂźen jehlen. SseĂȘfaven i medden ssĂȘur, akked wayen id irsen, di Babil, ar lmalayek Harut akked Marut. Ur sselmaden yiwen, mebla ma nnan: \"nekwni n$ewwu kan, ur jehhel\"! ĂĂĂĂefven, $uĂŽsen, amek ara ssemfaĂŽaqen argaz akked tmeĂźĂźut is. Ur ĂźĂźurun yiwen syis, siwa ma Ib$a Ăebbi. ĂĂĂĂefven ara ten ivuĂŽĂŽen, ur ten ineffaĂą. Ni$ Ă©ĂŽan ar win i p iu$en, ur as illi umur di laxeĂŽt. War ccekk, ard ucmit wayen is zzenzen leĂŽwaĂȘ nnsen, lemmer Ă©ĂŽin"
