  2,111,"Nnan: \"ur ikeĂ§Ă§em Loennet, siwa win illan d uday, ne$ d amasiĂȘi\". D wagi ay d asirem nnsen. Ini: \"awit ed atebbet nnwen, ma tessawalem tidep"
