  2,125,"Mi Nerra Axxam d lemqam i yimdanen, u d amkan n laman: \"erret lemqam n IbĂŽahim d loamaĂą\"! NĂąuhed i IbĂŽahim akked IsmaĂąil: \"zzizdget Axxam iW, i wid idewwiĂŽen, wid ip$imin, wid iĂźĂźinizen, wid ikennun"
