  2,133,"Ne$ tellam d inagan mi d ters tmeppant ar YaĂąqub, mi inna i tarwa s: \"anwa ara tĂąabdem deffir i\"? Nnan: \"a naĂąbed Ăebbi k, u Ăebbi n lejdud ik: IbĂŽahim, IsmaĂąil, IsĂȘaq. Ăebbi Yiwen. Nekwni nunez aS"
